text: Tomiris Kenenbayeva (born 20 July 1998) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== * 18th FINA World Championships 2019 Preliminary Round - Group C * 18th FINA World Championships 2019 ESP 18 - 6 KAZ Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
